    <title>About-Git</title>
    <link href="/2022/07/02/About-Git/"/>
    <url>/2022/07/02/About-Git/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="配置无密钥登录"><a href="#配置无密钥登录" class="headerlink" title="配置无密钥登录"></a>配置无密钥登录</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> id_rsa.pub  <br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="复制公钥之后粘贴到这里"><a href="#复制公钥之后粘贴到这里" class="headerlink" title="复制公钥之后粘贴到这里"></a>复制公钥之后粘贴到这里</h4><p><img src="C:/Users/ADMINI~1/AppData/Local/Temp/1656770357265.png" alt="1656770357265"></p><p>之后选中你要git clone 的仓库  </p><h3 id="在指定目录下"><a href="#在指定目录下" class="headerlink" title="在指定目录下"></a>在指定目录下</h3><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">git <span class="hljs-keyword">clone</span>  <span class="hljs-title">&#x27;&#x27; 这里跟ssh</span> 地址 &#x27;&#x27;<br>git init 初始化 在当前目录新建一个Git代码库<br>git add  . (. 表示所有文件 或者可以指定需要单独提交文件)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 通过add只是将文件或目录添加到了index暂存区，使用commit可以实现将暂存区的文件提交到本地仓库。</span><br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot; 这里是提交说明&quot;</span><br>git push <br><span class="hljs-comment">#本地的master分支推送到origin主机，同时指定origin为默认主机，后面就可以不加任何参数使用git push了，-u 参数指定一个默认主机</span><br>git push -u origin <span class="hljs-keyword">master</span><br><span class="hljs-title">克隆版本库的时候，所使用的远程主机自动被Git</span>命名为origin。如果想用其他的主机名，需要用git clone命令的-o选项指定。<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#查看指定文件状态</span><br>git status [filename]<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#查看所有文件状态</span><br>git status<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 新建一个分支，但依然停留在当前分支，使用：</span><br>git branch [branch-name]<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 切换分支</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果name为-则为上一个分支</span><br><br><br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:/Users/ADMINI~1/AppData/Local/Temp/1656770632965.png" alt="1656770632965"></p><h3 id="下面是我参考的链接"><a href="#下面是我参考的链接" class="headerlink" title="下面是我参考的链接"></a>下面是我参考的链接</h3><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>www.cnblogs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/syp172654682/</span>p/<span class="hljs-number">7689328</span>.html<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
